.TH JSH 1 "2026" "The-JLC-Project" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
jsh \- Jamie's Shell
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B jsh
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B jsh
is a minimal interactive shell supporting command execution, pipes, and
basic builtins. It uses GNU readline for line editing and history.
.SH BUILTINS
.TP
.B cd \fIdirectory\fR
Change the current working directory.
.TP
.B exit
Exit the shell.
.SH FEATURES
.TP
.B Pipes
Single pipe operator
.B |
is supported between two commands.
.TP
.B History
Command history is maintained via GNU readline.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Normal exit via the
.B exit
builtin.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR sh (1),
.BR bash (1),
.BR readline (3)
.SH AUTHORS
The-JLC-Project contributors.
